            <div type="translation">
            <p> Petrui [wife] of Telmu</p></div>

            <div type="commentary">
            <p>A nearly identical urn for Telmu can be found at PA.Phil.UP.UM.E.MS3428. In our case,
                    Petrui, likely a freeborn Etruscan woman, took her husband's new surname
                    acquired upon his manumission. Telmu and Petrui had likely prospered in life and
                    attained a certain social standing.</p></div>
            

